This folder contains a webApp sample developed in PHP, for practical aim.
Duplex Drive is a web application that allows any car dealership to easily and efficiently manage the purchase and rental of their vehicles. Through a quick and streamlined interaction, it encourages users to place an order without requiring lengthy bureaucratic procedures that might discourage customers. It also provides a tool for administrators (dealership employees) and a dedicated section for the company owner.

For the installation (XAMPP and Composer are required):

Download the code directly into the htdocs folder.

Extract the .zip folder.

Rename the folder to DuplexDrive.

Run "composer install" from the terminal inside the project folder.

Open the "config/config" file and modify the database access credentials.
